There used to be a cleaver fox in the forest.
one day it started to think deep about its future survival and came up with a plan.
Gathered all the animals in the forest and started weaving a story.
It was about the guardian of the forest, honours and who can be the guardian.
In the starting all other animals are quite confused about the proposal.
Then fox started explaining that there will be a new animal in the forest which looks more dangerous and will guard the forest.
it will look like a fox but in a blue colour.
Every animal was surprised and thought fox has lost its mind and dispersed from gathering.
